  <summary>4/29/1988--Introduced.
Amends the Internal Revenue Code to provide that the income tax rules requiring cost capitalization shall not apply to the qualified artistic work expenses of freelance writers, artists, and photographers. Excludes from qualified expenses those related to printing, photographic plates, motion picture films, video tapes, and similar items.</summary>
